text: @Keir_Starmer This is excellent news. We also send thanks to @JeremyCorbyn. The difference he made has been greatly underestimated.  Meanwhile, we all need to work together to defeat two viruses, not only #coronavirus but also the resurgence of Thatcherism, another great evil..
